Folder Structure Describe:

Connection/
    Connection folder hold mongodb connection info

Controller/
    Controller folder hold all controller file 
        admin/ hold all admin panel api related controller

Helper/
    For global helper

Middleware
    Hold Middleware of api and whole project

Model/
    Only hold model of mongo schema

Route/
    hold all route 
        admin.js:   hold all admin panel routes
        api.js: hold all mobile api routes

Schema/
    Hold all schema files for mongo collection

Validation/
    hold validation for all api
    